    "description": "B-RAIN is a game to avoid bullets by matching its color with its color.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901610/extras/6dbed4b097c5dbe7397bca44e1f767c5.poster.avif?t=1646174811\" width=504 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901610/extras/6dbed4b097c5dbe7397bca44e1f767c5.webm?t=1646174811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901610/extras/6dbed4b097c5dbe7397bca44e1f767c5.mp4?t=1646174811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>The player can change the color of the immovable square in the center to four.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901610/extras/d40e6418943e3d4e479591a737d3d07b.avif?t=1646174811\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>You can avoid matching colors with bullets flying in random colors among the four colors.<br>Of course, if you touch a bullet in a different color, you will die.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901610/extras/78d2d44157252c748c07add6fda6abaf.avif?t=1646174811\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br>I hope you survive as long as possible!",
